      <title>埃及总统塞西下令组建新政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/egyptian-president-el-sisi-orders-formation-of-new-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西命令总理穆斯塔法·马德布利组建新政府，目前这个北非国家在获得超过 500 亿美元的援助和投资后正在推进全面的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/egyptian-president-el-sisi-orders-formation-of-new-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:43:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
