      <title>沙特阿拉伯第一季度交易量跌至三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/saudi-arabia-first-quarter-deal-flow-slumps-to-three-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯第一季度完成的投资交易数量为 2021 年以来最少，这进一步表明该国难以吸引私营企业和外国投资者的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/saudi-arabia-first-quarter-deal-flow-slumps-to-three-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:06:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称俄罗斯寻求法国在尼日尔持有的铀资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russia-said-to-seek-takeover-of-france-s-uranium-assets-in-niger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，俄罗斯正寻求接管一家法国国有企业在尼日尔持有的铀资产，此举将进一步挑战西方在非洲的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russia-said-to-seek-takeover-of-france-s-uranium-assets-in-niger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政局动荡 投资者忧心忡忡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非大选未能产生绝对胜利者，联盟谈判结果和未来政策方向仍存在很大不确定性，投资者准备迎接南非金融市场的进一步动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
